---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Base
    title="Company — KYDE"
    description="We're building governance infrastructure for the most important technology shift of our lifetime."
>
    <Navbar />

    <main>

        <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 md:pt-48 md:pb-36">
            <div class="bg-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

                <div class="mb-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-500 shrink-0"></span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300">↳ Company</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-px w-full bg-zinc-800"></div>
                </div>

                <h1 class="hero-h1 max-w-5xl text-5xl text-white uppercase tracking-tight md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
                    We're building governance infrastructure for the most important
                    <span class="gradient-text"> technology shift of our lifetime.</span>
                </h1>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ BODY ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative border-t border-zinc-800/60 py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-white">About</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-600">[KYDE]</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-8 max-w-2xl">
                        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
                            AI will transform everything — healthcare, energy, finance, critical infrastructure, the way entire organizations operate. This isn't speculation. It's already happening.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
                            But the path from here to AI-first enterprises runs through existing infrastructure — production systems, regulated environments, legal frameworks, and organizations built for human decision-making. Bringing autonomous agents into that world safely, verifiably, and at scale is an unsolved infrastructure problem.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
                            That's what Kyde builds. The operational layer that lets organizations deploy autonomous agents into critical infrastructure with the same rigor they apply to their networks, their keys, and their data centers. A cryptographic root of trust for every agent action. Fleet management that treats agents like the workforce they are.
                        </p>

                        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-400/60 pl-6 py-1">
                            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
                                We believe the companies that define this layer now will define how the agentic economy works for decades. We intend to be that foundation.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">
                            Early stage. Based in Germany. Building for the industries where failure has consequences.
                        </p>

                        <div class="pt-4">
                            <a
                                href="mailto:hello@kyde.com"
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-700 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-300 hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-all"
                            >
                                hello@kyde.com
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />
</Base>
